page.title: 20SIGNING OFF FROM TICKHILL
page.content:
The information shown on this disc was compiled by pupils in their final year at Tickhill Estfeld First/Middle School:
Darren Bagley,Stephen Bowskill,Andrew Brown,Trevor Davies,Stuart Davy,Carl Fox,Richard Frith,Christopher Grocock,Mark Hanman,Mark Jackson,Owen Nettleship,Lee Scholes,Christopher Temporal,Paul Turner,Robert Walker, Scott Warbrick,Robert Westmorland, Deborah Birch,Clare Bradley,Dawn Carr Sarah Fenn,Helena Garritt,Emma Gibson Chloe Goddard,Angela Guest,Michelle Naylor,Julie Thornton,Suzanne Winfield,Janine Copley,Rachel Welburn and Paul Graham who did a great deal of the work but has since emigrated to New Zealand.Jeremy Threadgold and Christopher Medcalf aged 9 also helped.
